---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="text-center py-24 px-6">
    <h2
      class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6"
      data-aos="fade-up"
    >
      About Us
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-delay="100"
    >
      We're not just a team — we're a unit. A bunch of friends who decided to
      build, break, and better the digital world together. We focus on what
      matters and back each other through the chaos.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-12"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        <img
          src="./aayush.webp"
          alt="Aayush Shukla"
          class="w-40 h-40 rounded-xl object-cover filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
        />
        <div class="text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Aayush</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-md">
            Connecting the backend and frontend, keeping the team together,
            planning projects, guiding everyone, and making sure the mission
            stays on course.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-600">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/a2ys"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://linkedin.com/in/a2ys"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com/unreal_sapien"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://a2ys.dev"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="250"
      >
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/400"
          alt="Koshambi"
          class="w-40 h-40 rounded-xl object-cover filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
        />
        <div class="text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Koshambi</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-md">
            Frontend pro who polishes every detail. If it's perfect, she makes
            it better. Code meets design, and neither stands a chance.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-600">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/koshambiB"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/koshambi-bardhan-62b83b2ab/"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-12"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="300"
      >
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/400"
          alt="Bhargavi"
          class="w-40 h-40 rounded-xl object-cover filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
        />
        <div class="text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Bhargavi</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-md">
            The backend mind that keeps it all glued. From clean architecture to
            team vibes, she holds it all together when it matters most.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-600">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/BhargaviD2"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bhargavideshmukhofficial/"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="350"
      >
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/400"
          alt="Amla"
          class="w-40 h-40 rounded-xl object-cover filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
        />
        <div class="text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Amal</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-md">
            Brains behind the AI. Always calm unless the computer's throwing
            shade — and even then, he's the one fixing it.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-600">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/amal0307"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/amal-m-raju-8b193718b/"
              target="_blank"
              class="hover:text-black transition"
              ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
